01:07:51,385 --> 01:07:53,154
There is nobody here.

564
01:07:53,645 --> 01:07:55,518
You can do nothing against us.

565
01:08:30,533 --> 01:08:31,652
Hello?

566
01:08:32,525 --> 01:08:33,724
Michel...

567
01:08:34,135 --> 01:08:35,812
What about Catherine?

568
01:08:43,613 --> 01:08:44,858
Yes.

569
01:08:46,578 --> 01:08:48,337
Yes, I'll be there.

570
01:08:50,972 --> 01:08:52,547
Alone.

571
01:09:19,096 --> 01:09:20,335
Give the girl back.

572
01:09:38,242 --> 01:09:39,601
Michel?

573
01:09:39,955 --> 01:09:41,610
Is that you?

574
01:09:51,383 --> 01:09:53,244
Mummy! Mummy!

575
01:09:55,509 --> 01:09:56,696
I beg you.

576
01:09:56,936 --> 01:09:58,563
Don't drink.

577
01:09:59,050 --> 01:10:00,306
Come on, darling...

578
01:10:00,523 --> 01:10:02,367
Don't drink!

579
01:10:03,734 --> 01:10:05,572
I need you.

580
01:10:06,414 --> 01:10:07,956
Leave me alone.

581
01:10:08,541 --> 01:10:10,656
I have the right to drink.

582
01:10:10,909 --> 01:10:13,704
I have the right to die.

583
01:10:16,094 --> 01:10:19,510
It's so good, you know,
sleeping, isn't it?

584
01:10:19,999 --> 01:10:22,188
Sleeping for ever.

585
01:10:24,304 --> 01:10:26,210
You're just like me.

586
01:10:27,442 --> 01:10:29,726
You'll end up just like me.

587
01:11:26,602 --> 01:11:27,584
Catherine!

588
01:11:28,522 --> 01:11:30,303
He's going to kill me!

589
01:11:34,026 --> 01:11:35,365
I love you, Véronique.

590
01:11:55,813 --> 01:11:56,886
I love you.

591
01:12:04,502 --> 01:12:06,432
We're leaving, the three of us.

592
01:12:37,182 --> 01:12:38,186
Beat it!

593
01:12:40,943 --> 01:12:42,987
Serves you right.

594
01:12:51,361 --> 01:12:52,525
Come on.

595
01:12:52,868 --> 01:12:54,152
Beat it!

596
01:13:15,996 --> 01:13:17,948
I've been waiting for you.

597
01:13:19,524 --> 01:13:21,739
I've been waiting for you
for a very long time.

598
01:13:23,320 --> 01:13:24,793
Let's play.

599
01:14:14,546 --> 01:14:15,974
You lost.

600
01:14:29,713 --> 01:14:31,312
Nuit d'Or!

601
01:14:32,214 --> 01:14:34,075
Give him his money back.

602
01:14:34,791 --> 01:14:36,356
Go away, Michel.

603
01:14:36,687 --> 01:14:39,248
I won't do anything against you.
And nobody will.

604
01:14:47,383 --> 01:14:49,221
Poor Pidoux...

605
01:14:59,190 --> 01:15:00,628
We are losers.

606
01:15:00,914 --> 01:15:02,581
Both of us.

607
01:15:04,243 --> 01:15:06,058
Marie doesnt love you.

608
01:15:07,199 --> 01:15:09,003
She never loved you.

609
01:15:10,237 --> 01:15:12,943
She became crazy
to never see you again.

610
01:15:14,473 --> 01:15:16,477
And never recognize you.

611
01:15:18,425 --> 01:15:20,662
How could anyone love you?

612
01:15:26,041 --> 01:15:28,039
You're going to kill me.

613
01:15:34,309 --> 01:15:36,387
This time, it will be for good.

614
01:15:37,231 --> 01:15:38,555
The real Michel Fournier.

615
01:15:41,895 --> 01:15:43,517
The show is over.

616
01:15:44,238 --> 01:15:46,251
No more faux-macabre.

617
01:15:52,246 --> 01:15:55,067
I am not a murderer.
I was wrongly accused.

618
01:15:55,626 --> 01:15:57,453
You always knew it.

619
01:16:28,394 --> 01:16:30,347
It wasn't loaded.

620
01:16:38,440 --> 01:16:40,621
It has never been loaded.
